@startuml Activity Diagram - Daily Learning Process (Swimlane)
|User|
start
:Open LangStar app;
|Frontend|
if (User authenticated?) then (yes)
    :Display Home Page;
else (no)
    :Show Sign In page;
    |User|
    :Enter credentials;
    |Frontend|
    :Validate input;
    :Send login request;
    |Backend API|
    :Receive /auth/login request;
    :Verify credentials;
    |Database|
    :Query user data;
    |Backend API|
    if (Credentials valid?) then (yes)
        :Generate JWT token;
        :Return success + token;
        |Frontend|
        :Store token;
        :Display Home Page;
    else (no)
        :Return error;
        |Frontend|
        :Show error message;
        stop
    endif
endif

|User|
:Navigate to Daily Learning;
|Frontend|
:Send /games_word/dailies request;
note right: Includes username, language
|Backend API|
:Receive request;
:Extract user info;
|Database|
:Fetch user points for language;
|Backend API|
:Determine user level;
:Call generate_dailies();
|External API|
:Gemini generates 10 flashcards;
note right: Based on language & level
|Backend API|
:Receive flashcards data;
:Return dailies to frontend;
|Frontend|
:Display first flashcard;
|User|
:View word/concept;
:Click pronounce button;
|Frontend|
:Send text to Sarvam API;
|External API|
:Sarvam generates audio;
|Frontend|
:Play pronunciation audio;
|User|
:Practice pronunciation;
:Click next/check button;
|Frontend|
repeat
    :Show next flashcard;
    |User|
    :Study and practice;
repeat while (More flashcards?)

|User|
:Complete all dailies;
|Frontend|
:Send /games/updatescore request;
note right: Award points for completion
|Backend API|
:Receive score update;
|Database|
:Update user language points;
|Backend API|
:Return success;
|Frontend|
:Show completion message;
:Update progress display;
|User|
:View updated progress;
stop
@enduml